Utterance.UttText: In bed 3 is Laurence Simpson, 69 yrs old under Dr Wen, he came in with chest pain and with long standing asthma and low blood pressure.
They are planning to do CABG, ballooning or angioplasty but hasn't decided on it yet.
He is a new admission today and so some of the assessment tools hasn't been done yet but admission paperworks have been done and medications have been ordered and given.
